'''Oxonmoot 2024''', the 51st annual [[Oxonmoot]] hosted by [[The Tolkien Society]], took place between [[29 August]] - [[1 September]] [[2024]]. As in the previous years, it was a hybrid event bringing together online delegates with those attending in person at St Ann's College, [[University of Oxford|Oxford]].
